{"type": "article", "id": 14561, "title": "Roger Vivier 香港开第三家店，以及，俄罗斯品牌把中国国旗穿上了身｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2015-09-07T08:54:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4105, "name": "联名系列"}, {"id": 796, "name": "球鞋"}, {"id": 31, "name": "英国"}, {"id": 193, "name": "香港"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 15621, "name": "Quiksilver"}, {"id": 15622, "name": "Gant"}, {"id": 10224, "name": "Roger Vivier"}, {"id": 15623, "name": "Gosha Rubchinskiy"}, {"id": 2840, "name": "Opening Ceremony"}, {"id": 14370, "name": "reebok"}, {"id": 4949, "name": "Guess"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607142005pZdSHqnEgcMruT7v.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t</p>\n<h3>\r\n\t\t一些重要的新闻：<span style=\"text-align:justify;\"></span> \r\n\t</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><a href=\"http://www.nofashion.cn/a/1441256271383.html\" target=\"_blank\">美国滑浪服饰零售商 Quiksilver 寻求出售</a></strong>｜因业绩不振今年股价暴跌 80% 而陷入摘牌危机，bloogberg 称 Quiksilver Inc. 现正与潜在战略投资者谈判，其目标是公司管理层融资进行收购，期望最大限度保留现有业务和门店，否则一旦清盘将不得不放弃昂贵的租约以吸引买家。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://wwd.com/menswear-news/retail-business/gant-rebranding-patrik-nilsson-10209204/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Gant 正着手品牌的重塑</strong></a>｜1949 年在美国纽黑文市创立的品牌 Gant，过去十年在海外的流行程度远超美国的。甚至从 2008 年起由瑞士公司 Maus Frères 控股，但目前新的总裁兼 CEO Patrik Nilsson 的上任，准备着手在美国本土的品牌战略。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.nofashion.cn/a/1441455667921.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>英国高街品牌跌入 6 年低点</strong></a>｜英国会计和商业顾问公司 BDO LLP 发布的 8 月份高街品牌销售数据亦显示英国高街零售市场陷入 2008 年以来的谷底。自 5 月份以来，英国高街品牌销售已经连续 4 个月下跌，而这样的情况是自 2009 年以来首次出现。受英国人在 8 月份选择度假情况增多影响，而英镑的坚挺和欧元的疲软也是英国人选择更多海外度假和欧元区消费。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://footwearnews.com/2015/fashion/designers/roger-vivier-hong-kong-store-capsule-collection-146412/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Roger Vivier 在香港开了第三家店</strong></a>｜在其它品牌放缓在亚洲区尤其是香港的扩张时，Roger Vivier 在香港利园二期开第三家门店，并推出庆祝开业的限量胶囊系列。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/fleet-street-cyn-luca-swim-outerwear10211095-10211095/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Fleet Street 收购 Cyn &amp; Luca</strong></a>｜为加强泳装线，1964 年就建立的品牌 <span>Fleet Street  又收购了新公司，使公司面向各层次需求人群。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t</p>\n<h3>\r\n\t\t一些值得一看的：\r\n\t</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tadidas 为庆祝美网公开赛，<a href=\"http://airows.com/style/adidas-celebrates-the-us-open-with-this-special-edition-stan-smith\" target=\"_blank\">推出限量版 Stan Smith</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://airows.com/style/adidas-celebrates-the-us-open-with-this-special-edition-stan-smith\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141956gfLIJeR2Ktv5z8Yc.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66774194\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://airows.com/style/adidas-celebrates-the-us-open-with-this-special-edition-stan-smith\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141956OzRcGy1F8Z29Khg5.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66774194\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://airows.com/style/adidas-celebrates-the-us-open-with-this-special-edition-stan-smith\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141957y3QKgwk67dUhDmzt.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66774194\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t看俄罗斯品牌 <a href=\"http://nowre.com/news/6420/e-luo-si-feng-wu-gosha-rubchinskiy-2015-qiu-dong-xi-lie\">Gosha Rubchinskiy</a> 把五星红旗和繁体字“运动”当时尚元素穿身上。美潮店 Opening Ceremony 最近为 Gosha Rubchinskiy 拍摄<a href=\"http://www.openingceremony.us/entry.asp?pid=12425\" target=\"_blank\">最新的 2015 秋冬系列look book</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141957Hjb5l8fgDFBxcMhN.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7444668\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071419584dDZME7iIWL5jYXK.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071419583moL8vVcxR42SETh.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141959c2DBPrLIHRFNzgVn.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141959X0pZ7bnF1JMe2QrN.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2015/09/05/asap-mob-guess-collaboration-teaser/\" target=\"_blank\">A$AP Mob x Guess 联名系列抢先看</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2015/09/05/asap-mob-guess-collaboration-teaser/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142000k8VItvRzq1bPnAKE.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://styleengine.com/2015/09/01/reebok-adds-a-gum-sole-to-3-of-their-classic-silhouettes/\" target=\"_blank\">reebok 推出三款全白皮制球鞋</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://styleengine.com/2015/09/01/reebok-adds-a-gum-sole-to-3-of-their-classic-silhouettes/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142000B2WyrnwmgO3v5hu0.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://styleengine.com/2015/09/01/reebok-adds-a-gum-sole-to-3-of-their-classic-silhouettes/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071420016TpPHXwV1quxMBKg.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://styleengine.com/2015/09/01/reebok-adds-a-gum-sole-to-3-of-their-classic-silhouettes/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071420012kZqOVngUsoPxdyA.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://styleengine.com/2015/09/01/reebok-adds-a-gum-sole-to-3-of-their-classic-silhouettes/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142002TbrPksxH3alBeFzg.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t日本独立牛仔潮牌 FDMTL 庆祝十周年，<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2015/09/06/vans-fdmtl/#slide-5\" target=\"_blank\">与 Vans 推出限量联名系列</a>，鞋面上是错落有致的靛蓝牛仔拼布。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142002liFwkjveGmPZcOpT.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142003UwIz6NupyFLWtR9X.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142003QLpCjl9871yGTEaY.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t</p>\n<h4>\r\n\t\t一些有意思的说法：\r\n\t</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tUber 要和电商联合，帮助线上零售平台、时尚电商网站直接送货到用户手上了？我们在<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/14549.html\" target=\"_blank\">另一篇更详细的文章</a>里为你解释这件事。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071420041nNKp0weu8lf7B94.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://styleengine.com/2015/09/01/reebok-adds-a-gum-sole-to-3-of-their-classic-silhouettes/\" target=\"_blank\"> </a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://styleengine.com/2015/09/01/reebok-adds-a-gum-sole-to-3-of-their-classic-silhouettes/\" target=\"_blank\"> </a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://styleengine.com/2015/09/01/reebok-adds-a-gum-sole-to-3-of-their-classic-silhouettes/\" target=\"_blank\"> </a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}